Bigger Tamriel Creatures Plugin Release by MrGenki

____________________________
Welcome folks,this a just a small plugin that makes \"Giants,Mammoths,Trolls and Horses\" about 2x times bigger

____________________________
Installation:
Just put the extracted file into your DATA folder

Note:
Works in version 1.5
